db
Class FileItem

java.lang.Object
  db.FileItem

public class FileItem
extends java.lang.Object

Class to represent a file element and allows converting between this and XML objects so that XML Node can be used in Database API. The negative size is stored as "unknown" in XML because Google Docs sets the size to -1. The Backup element is stored as a Node.

Author:
Mamta
